      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "AUTAFINNA (6) made a courageous debut on the heavy (10) surface with a closing second over 1600m at this track. Looks to have more upside than most of these and expected to go close. SMOKEY SAINT (5) finished in the minor money at his last three outings and a win looks imminent. Took control early on the good surface with a game third over 2220m at Grafton. On the backup and best figures measure up. SEND A TELEGRAM (4) showed good early dash and gripped on late with a plugging fourth over 1614m at this track. Jumps further in trip in a very average contest. Place preferred. ELITE DELIGHT (8) is fourth up now and liked the way she closed late with a tidy fifth over 1750m at Muswellbrook. Can race closer from the draw and stays in the calculations.",
